                        <p><hi rend="italic">Note:</hi> The following factors have been considered
                            in arriving at the proposed basic quotas: <list>
                                <label>1.</label>
                                <item>Average total exports from each country during recent
                                    years.</item>
                                <label>2.</label>
                                <item>Average exports to United States during recent years.</item>
                                <pb facs="0411" n="399" xml:id="pg_399"/>
                                <label>3.</label>
                                <item>Requirements of United States market for special types of
                                    coffee.</item>
                                <label>4.</label>
                                <item>Normal markets for each country’s coffee.</item>
                                <label>5.</label>
                                <item>Abnormal conditions due to war.</item>
                            </list></p>
